Subsections (1) to (5) of this section are subject to:
Subsection (7) of this section and the other provisions of this part of this article;
KRS 355.4-210 with respect to a security interest of a collecting bank;
KRS 355.5-118 with respect to a security interest of an issuer or nominated person; and
KRS 355.9-110 with respect to a security interest arising under Article 2 or 2A of this chapter.
